  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kosmo Skirmish is a multiplayer space combat game. Choose your arsenal carefully to take down your opponents!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813340/extras/13bbdaba36c06eec83d1c024dc5e17a9.apng?t=1732514037\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813340/extras/13bbdaba36c06eec83d1c024dc5e17a9.poster.avif?t=1732514037\" class=\"bb_img\" width=192 height=48 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From 2 to 8 players: Online, locally - or both at the same time </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally generated destructible terrain</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select your equipment of 4 weapons from an arsenal of 12 weapons and tools</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several game modes: Each for themselves or as a team</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hostile environments: Lava rise, death laser, meteorites, gas balls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game settings: victory points, time, placement</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kosmo Skirmish is a multiplayer space combat game. Choose your arsenal carefully to take down your opponents!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813340/extras/13bbdaba36c06eec83d1c024dc5e17a9.apng?t=1732514037\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813340/extras/13bbdaba36c06eec83d1c024dc5e17a9.poster.avif?t=1732514037\" class=\"bb_img\" width=192 height=48 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From 2 to 8 players: Online, locally - or both at the same time </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally generated destructible terrain</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select your equipment of 4 weapons from an arsenal of 12 weapons and tools</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several game modes: Each for themselves or as a team</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hostile environments: Lava rise, death laser, meteorites, gas balls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game settings: victory points, time, placement</p></li></ul>",
